{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"8e26e8749bccd9d3739356","title":"蜂鸣/旋律 MQTT 协同与 TCM 内存优化开发记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367060,"created":1780371330026,"custom":{},"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-27_蜂鸣旋律MQTT协同与TCM内存优化开发记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"a4a0e353526652354f95ededd4058460","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-27_蜂鸣旋律MQTT协同与TCM内存优化开发记录","id":"8e26e8749bccd9d3739356","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-18_按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":10,"offset":149},"end":{"line":7,"column":45,"offset":184},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-18_按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录"}},{"from":{"fname":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲","id":"62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":39,"offset":3788},"end":{"line":31,"column":81,"offset":3830},"indent":[]},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-27_蜂鸣旋律MQTT协同与TCM内存优化开发记录"},{"from":{"fname":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲","id":"62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":90,"offset":4725},"end":{"line":46,"column":132,"offset":4767},"indent":[]},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-27_蜂鸣旋律MQTT协同与TCM内存优化开发记录"}],"anchors":{"蜂鸣旋律-mqtt-协同与-tcm-内存优化开发记录":{"type":"header","text":"蜂鸣/旋律 MQTT 协同与 TCM 内存优化开发记录","value":"蜂鸣旋律-mqtt-协同与-tcm-内存优化开发记录","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"1-背景":{"type":"header","text":"1. 背景","value":"1-背景","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"2-改动文件清单":{"type":"header","text":"2. 改动文件清单","value":"2-改动文件清单","line":33,"column":0,"depth":2},"3-问题与根因":{"type":"header","text":"3. 问题与根因","value":"3-问题与根因","line":51,"column":0,"depth":2},"31-音量volumeset-对按键无效":{"type":"header","text":"3.1 音量：volumeSet 对按键无效","value":"31-音量volumeset-对按键无效","line":53,"column":0,"depth":3},"32-旋律失真卡顿dma-指针复用":{"type":"header","text":"3.2 旋律失真、卡顿（DMA 指针复用）","value":"32-旋律失真卡顿dma-指针复用","line":58,"column":0,"depth":3},"33-tcm-堆耗尽--打印线程创建失败":{"type":"header","text":"3.3 TCM 堆耗尽 → 打印线程创建失败","value":"33-tcm-堆耗尽--打印线程创建失败","line":64,"column":0,"depth":3},"34-mqtt-同步收包与旋律争抢-cpu":{"type":"header","text":"3.4 MQTT 同步收包与旋律争抢 CPU","value":"34-mqtt-同步收包与旋律争抢-cpu","line":83,"column":0,"depth":3},"35-日志误报-rx-dispatch-failed":{"type":"header","text":"3.5 日志误报 rx dispatch failed","value":"35-日志误报-rx-dispatch-failed","line":88,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-技术方案":{"type":"header","text":"4. 技术方案","value":"4-技术方案","line":95,"column":0,"depth":2},"41-按键与旋律音量分离":{"type":"header","text":"4.1 按键与旋律音量分离","value":"41-按键与旋律音量分离","line":97,"column":0,"depth":3},"42-旋律-dma-乒乓与背压":{"type":"header","text":"4.2 旋律 DMA 乒乓与背压","value":"42-旋律-dma-乒乓与背压","line":118,"column":0,"depth":3},"43-tcm-内存优化本次核心":{"type":"header","text":"4.3 TCM 内存优化（本次核心）","value":"43-tcm-内存优化本次核心","line":135,"column":0,"depth":3},"44-线程优先级与-mqtt-协同":{"type":"header","text":"4.4 线程优先级与 MQTT 协同","value":"44-线程优先级与-mqtt-协同","line":158,"column":0,"depth":3},"45-收图--打印衔接":{"type":"header","text":"4.5 收图 → 打印衔接","value":"45-收图--打印衔接","line":173,"column":0,"depth":3},"46-日志与返回值":{"type":"header","text":"4.6 日志与返回值","value":"46-日志与返回值","line":186,"column":0,"depth":3},"5-内存与资源一览":{"type":"header","text":"5. 内存与资源一览","value":"5-内存与资源一览","line":193,"column":0,"depth":2},"51-旋律相关":{"type":"header","text":"5.1 旋律相关","value":"51-旋律相关","line":195,"column":0,"depth":3},"52-典型峰值收图打印时":{"type":"header","text":"5.2 典型峰值（收图打印时）","value":"52-典型峰值收图打印时","line":204,"column":0,"depth":3},"6-业务集成关系":{"type":"header","text":"6. 业务集成关系","value":"6-业务集成关系","line":211,"column":0,"depth":2},"7-注意事项与已知约束":{"type":"header","text":"7. 注意事项与已知约束","value":"7-注意事项与已知约束","line":237,"column":0,"depth":2},"8-验证建议":{"type":"header","text":"8. 验证建议","value":"8-验证建议","line":251,"column":0,"depth":2},"9-相关源码路径":{"type":"header","text":"9. 相关源码路径","value":"9-相关源码路径","line":261,"column":0,"depth":2},"10-变更摘要相对-2026-05-18":{"type":"header","text":"10. 变更摘要（相对 2026-05-18）","value":"10-变更摘要相对-2026-05-18","line":279,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"x43b2g7jzkj4yilx9xlswpb","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"蜂鸣旋律-mqtt-协同与-tcm-内存优化开发记录\">蜂鸣/旋律 MQTT 协同与 TCM 内存优化开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#蜂鸣旋律-mqtt-协同与-tcm-内存优化开发记录\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"蜂鸣旋律-mqtt-协同与-tcm-内存优化开发记录-1\">蜂鸣/旋律 MQTT 协同与 TCM 内存优化开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#蜂鸣旋律-mqtt-协同与-tcm-内存优化开发记录-1\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>日期</strong>：2026-05-27<br>\n<strong>工程</strong>：<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd_bz</code><br>\n<strong>编译命令</strong>：<code>scons --beken=bk7252n -j8</code><br>\n<strong>前置文档</strong>：<a href=\"/notes/238cee9d6e5d3351d1562b\">按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录</a>（初版 beep 模块与旋律架构）</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-背景\">1. 背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>在初版「按键蜂鸣 + 生图等待旋律」落地后，联调 MQTT 语音生图链路时出现一系列问题：</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>现象</th><th>影响</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>云端 <code>volumeSet</code> 后按键「滴滴」音量不变</td><td>用户误以为音量设置无效</td></tr><tr><td>旋律音量调节后出现沙沙声、卡顿</td><td>体验差，疑似音频链路异常</td></tr><tr><td>MQTT 同步收 <code>audioChunk</code> 时旋律断续</td><td>生图等待 BGM 不稳定</td></tr><tr><td>日志 <code>rx dispatch failed</code></td><td>误导排障（实际收包成功）</td></tr><tr><td><strong><code>create print thread failed</code></strong></td><td>收图完成后无法启动 <code>mqtt_prn</code> 打印线程，业务中断</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>根因集中在：<strong>音量策略未分离</strong>、<strong>DAC DMA 异步复用同一块缓冲</strong>、<strong>大数组常驻 BSS 挤占 TCM 堆</strong>、<strong>MQTT 收包线程长时间占用 CPU</strong>。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-改动文件清单\">2. 改动文件清单<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-改动文件清单\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>文件</th><th>改动类型</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>applications/button_control/beep.c</code></td><td>修改</td><td>按键/旋律音量分离；DMA 乒乓 + <code>tx_complete</code> 背压；旋律缓冲改为运行时分配；缩小 chunk/缓冲深度</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/button_control/beep.h</code></td><td>修改</td><td><code>beep_set_volume()</code> 文档：仅影响等待旋律</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_message.c</code></td><td>已有</td><td><code>volumeSet</code> → <code>beep_set_volume()</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/device_config.c</code></td><td>已有</td><td>配置加载时同步 <code>beep_set_volume()</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/main.c</code></td><td>已有</td><td>启动时从 <code>device_config_get_volume()</code> 初始化旋律音量</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/audio/audio_result_wait.c</code></td><td>已有</td><td>等待生图时 <code>beep_melody_start/stop</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/binary_rx/mqtt_backend_binary_audio_chunk.c</code></td><td>修改</td><td>收包/写 Flash 路径 <code>rt_thread_yield()</code>；收图完成前 <code>beep_melody_stop()</code> + 延时；修正返回值</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_async_rx.c</code></td><td>修改</td><td>同步收包模式 dispatch 前后 <code>yield</code>；<code>audioChunk</code> 成功路径不再误报失败</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_config.h</code></td><td>配置</td><td><code>CFG_MQTT_BACKEND_ASYNC_RX=0</code>（大图不能异步队列，防 OOM）</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_client.c</code></td><td>修改</td><td>Paho 线程优先级下调，为 <code>audio_th</code> 让出 CPU</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/binary_rx/mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c</code></td><td>相关</td><td><code>mqtt_prn</code> 线程创建（栈 6144）</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-问题与根因\">3. 问题与根因<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-问题与根因\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"31-音量volumeset-对按键无效\">3.1 音量：<code>volumeSet</code> 对按键无效<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#31-音量volumeset-对按键无效\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>beep_set_volume()</code> 原先同时影响按键蜂鸣与旋律，或仅改软件变量未区分通路。</li>\n<li><strong>产品要求</strong>：按键固定 <strong>65</strong>；旋律跟随配置文件 / <code>volumeSet</code>（0~100）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"32-旋律失真卡顿dma-指针复用\">3.2 旋律失真、卡顿（DMA 指针复用）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#32-旋律失真卡顿dma-指针复用\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>rt_device_write()</code> 在 DAC 驱动中<strong>只保存缓冲区指针</strong>，由 GDMA 异步读取（<code>GDMA_X_SRC_DTCM_RD_REQ</code>）。</li>\n<li>早期单块 <code>s_stereo_chunk</code> 在循环中被覆盖 → 杂音、断续。</li>\n<li>曾用 <code>s_stereo_chunks[8][1024]</code> 做乒乓，但 <strong>16KB 常驻 BSS</strong>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"33-tcm-堆耗尽--打印线程创建失败\">3.3 TCM 堆耗尽 → 打印线程创建失败<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#33-tcm-堆耗尽--打印线程创建失败\"></a></h3>\n<p>BK7252N 内存模型（<code>drivers/board.h</code> + <code>link.lds</code>）：</p>\n<pre><code>[ RAM: .data + .bss ... ] → _empty_ram → [ TCM 堆 → 256KB 末端 ]\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><code>rt_malloc</code> / <code>rt_thread_create</code> 栈均走 <strong>TCM 堆</strong>（<code>RT_KERNEL_MALLOC</code> → <code>tcm_malloc</code>）。</li>\n<li><code>s_stereo_chunks</code> 占 <strong>0x4000（16KB）BSS</strong>，直接压缩 <code>_empty_ram</code> 之后的可用堆。</li>\n<li>收图峰值：MQTT 缓冲 + LVGL + <code>mqtt_prn</code> 栈（6144）+ 其它线程 → <strong><code>rt_thread_create(\"mqtt_prn\", ...)</code> 失败</strong>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code>out/rtthread.map</code> 摘录（优化前）：</p>\n<pre><code>.bss.s_stereo_chunks    0x00408488    0x4000    beep.o\n_empty_ram              0x004292b8\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"34-mqtt-同步收包与旋律争抢-cpu\">3.4 MQTT 同步收包与旋律争抢 CPU<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#34-mqtt-同步收包与旋律争抢-cpu\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>CFG_MQTT_BACKEND_ASYNC_RX=0</code>：Paho 回调内同步处理 <code>audioChunk</code>，单次处理可达数百毫秒。</li>\n<li>若 <code>audio_th</code> 优先级过低，无法及时 <code>write</code> / 响应 <code>tx_complete</code>，旋律 underflow。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"35-日志误报-rx-dispatch-failed\">3.5 日志误报 <code>rx dispatch failed</code><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#35-日志误报-rx-dispatch-failed\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>audioChunk</code> 处理函数在「无需 JSON 应答」场景曾返回 <code>-1</code>。</li>\n<li><code>mqtt_backend_async_rx_push()</code> 在同步模式下将 <code>dispatch != 0</code> 视为失败并打印错误，<strong>实际收包与 Flash 写入已成功</strong>。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-技术方案\">4. 技术方案<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-技术方案\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"41-按键与旋律音量分离\">4.1 按键与旋律音量分离<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#41-按键与旋律音量分离\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">BEEP_FIXED_VOLUME</span>   <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">65</span>   </span><span class=\"token comment\">/* 按键蜂鸣，不随 volumeSet 变化 */</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> s_melody_volume <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">65</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 旋律，beep_set_volume / 配置文件 */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">beep_play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">beep_apply_fixed_codec_volume</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dac<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">/* CODEC_CMD_SET_VOLUME = 65 */</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">beep_melody_start</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">melody_apply_codec_volume</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dac<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>      <span class=\"token comment\">/* volume * 99 / 100，钳位 0~99 */</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>不再</strong>在旋律循环内对每块 PCM 做软件缩放（曾引入沙沙声）。</li>\n<li>音量仅通过 Codec 硬件 <code>CODEC_CMD_SET_VOLUME</code> 设置。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"42-旋律-dma-乒乓与背压\">4.2 旋律 DMA 乒乓与背压<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#42-旋律-dma-乒乓与背压\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>参数</th><th>初版（问题版）</th><th>当前值</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>CHUNK_MONO</code></td><td>512（32ms×2 立体声点）</td><td><strong>256</strong></td></tr><tr><td><code>MELODY_BUF_COUNT</code></td><td>8</td><td><strong>4</strong></td></tr><tr><td>缓冲存放</td><td><code>static int16_t s_stereo_chunks[8][1024]</code></td><td><strong><code>rt_malloc</code> 池，停止后 <code>rt_free</code></strong></td></tr><tr><td>常驻 RAM</td><td>16KB BSS</td><td><strong>0</strong>（空闲时）</td></tr><tr><td>播放中 RAM</td><td>16KB</td><td><strong>4KB</strong>（4×256×2×sizeof(int16_t)）</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>流程要点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>melody_tx_done</code>：<code>tx_complete</code> 时 <code>rt_sem_release(&#x26;s_tx_done_sem)</code>。</li>\n<li><code>melody_write_one_chunk</code>：当 <code>pipeline >= MELODY_BUF_COUNT - 1</code> 时 <code>rt_sem_take</code> 等待 DMA 消费，避免覆盖在途缓冲。</li>\n<li>启动时预填 <code>MELODY_BUF_COUNT - 2</code> 块，降低起播间隙。</li>\n<li>mono → stereo 展开：<code>chunk[j*2] = chunk[j*2+1] = MELODY_PCM[...]</code>。</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"43-tcm-内存优化本次核心\">4.3 TCM 内存优化（本次核心）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#43-tcm-内存优化本次核心\"></a></h3>\n<p><strong>策略</strong>：旋律缓冲<strong>仅在播放期间</strong>从 TCM 堆分配，停止后释放，避免 16KB 永久占用 BSS。</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">int16_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>s_stereo_chunk_pool <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> RT_NULL<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">rt_bool_t</span> <span class=\"token function\">melody_chunks_alloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    s_stereo_chunk_pool <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">int16_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token function\">rt_malloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>MELODY_POOL_BYTES<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">/* 4096 */</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">melody_chunks_free</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">rt_free</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_stereo_chunk_pool<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    s_stereo_chunk_pool <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> RT_NULL<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><code>BEEP_CMD_MELODY_START</code> 路径：<code>alloc</code> → 循环写 DAC → <code>close</code> → <code>free</code>。</li>\n<li>收图完成路径（<code>mqtt_backend_binary_audio_chunk.c</code>）在创建打印线程前调用 <code>beep_melody_stop()</code> + <code>rt_thread_mdelay(100)</code>，确保音频线程退出循环并 <strong>释放 4KB 池</strong>，再 <code>rt_thread_create(\"mqtt_prn\", 6144, ...)</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>效果</strong>：永久释放约 <strong>16KB TCM 堆</strong>；播放中峰值从 16KB 降至 <strong>4KB</strong>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"44-线程优先级与-mqtt-协同\">4.4 线程优先级与 MQTT 协同<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#44-线程优先级与-mqtt-协同\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>线程</th><th>优先级（数值越小越高）</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>audio_th</code></td><td><strong>14</strong></td><td>须高于 Paho / 收包路径，及时喂 DMA</td></tr><tr><td>Paho MQTT</td><td><strong>20</strong>（下调）</td><td>避免长时间霸占 CPU</td></tr><tr><td><code>mqproc</code></td><td>20</td><td>仅 <code>CFG_MQTT_BACKEND_ASYNC_RX=1</code> 时存在</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>同步收包优化（<code>mqtt_backend_async_rx.c</code>）：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>mqtt_backend_rx_dispatch_payload()</code> 入口、出口各 <code>rt_thread_yield()</code>。</li>\n<li><code>mqtt_backend_binary_audio_chunk.c</code> 写 Flash 循环内 <code>rt_thread_yield()</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>异步 RX 保持关闭</strong>：<code>CFG_MQTT_BACKEND_ASYNC_RX=0</code>。大图分片若入队会额外 malloc，易 OOM。</p>\n<h3 id=\"45-收图--打印衔接\">4.5 收图 → 打印衔接<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#45-收图--打印衔接\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* mqtt_backend_binary_audio_chunk.c — result 帧处理末尾 */</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">beep_melody_stop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">rt_thread_mdelay</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">mqtt_backend_binary_spawn_print_thread</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">rt_kprintf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mqtt backend create print thread failed\\r\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"46-日志与返回值\">4.6 日志与返回值<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#46-日志与返回值\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>mqtt_backend_binary_audio_chunk</code> 正常结束 <strong><code>return 0</code></strong>，避免同步 push 误报 <code>rx dispatch failed</code>。</li>\n<li><code>audioChunk</code> 无 MQTT JSON 应答属正常，不应返回失败码给 dispatch 层。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-内存与资源一览\">5. 内存与资源一览<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-内存与资源一览\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"51-旋律相关\">5.1 旋律相关<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#51-旋律相关\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>资源</th><th>位置</th><th>大小</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>MELODY_PCM[]</code></td><td>Flash（<code>melody_pcm_data.h</code>）</td><td>~68KB</td><td>34400×int16，不占用 RAM</td></tr><tr><td><code>beep_buf</code></td><td>TCM 堆（<code>audio_th</code> 内 <code>rt_malloc</code>）</td><td>~2.4KB</td><td>按键 PCM，线程生命周期常驻</td></tr><tr><td><code>s_stereo_chunk_pool</code></td><td>TCM 堆（旋律播放时）</td><td><strong>4KB</strong></td><td>停止后释放</td></tr><tr><td><code>audio_th</code> 栈</td><td>TCM 堆</td><td>4096</td><td>创建时分配</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h3 id=\"52-典型峰值收图打印时\">5.2 典型峰值（收图打印时）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#52-典型峰值收图打印时\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>旋律已停、缓冲已释放 → TCM 可用于 <code>mqtt_prn</code>（栈 6144）及运行时 MQTT/LVGL 缓冲。</li>\n<li>若仍 OOM：用 <code>list_memheap</code> / map 继续排查其它大块分配（如 <code>print_buf</code>、LVGL draw_buf）。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"6-业务集成关系\">6. 业务集成关系<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#6-业务集成关系\"></a></h2>\n<pre><code>语音上传完成 → audio_result_wait_start()\n              → beep_melody_start()     // 循环 C 大调琶音\n\nMQTT audioChunk 分片收包（同步，yield）\n              → Flash 落盘\n\nresult 帧 OK  → beep_melody_stop()\n              → mdelay(100)\n              → mqtt_prn 打印线程\n\n超时/失败     → audio_result_wait_clear() → beep_melody_stop()\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>API / 配置</th><th>作用</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>beep_play()</code></td><td>按键「叮咚」，Codec 音量 <strong>65</strong></td></tr><tr><td><code>beep_set_volume(v)</code></td><td>仅旋律；<code>volumeSet</code> / <code>device_config</code> / <code>main</code> 初始化</td></tr><tr><td><code>beep_set_muted()</code></td><td>P37 录音期间静音按键与旋律</td></tr><tr><td><code>beep_melody_start/stop()</code></td><td>生图等待 BGM</td></tr><tr><td><code>CFG_BEEP_MELODY_ENABLE</code></td><td>编译期裁剪旋律（默认 1）</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"7-注意事项与已知约束\">7. 注意事项与已知约束<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#7-注意事项与已知约束\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>DMA 源地址须在 DTCM/TCM 可达范围</strong>：旋律池使用 <code>rt_malloc</code>（TCM 堆），满足 <code>GDMA_X_SRC_DTCM_RD_REQ</code>；不宜改为 SDRAM 除非驱动支持且实测通过。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>缓冲变浅</strong>：<code>CHUNK_MONO=256</code>、<code>MELODY_BUF_COUNT=4</code> 后，MQTT 同步大包收图时旋律抗抖动余量小于旧版 8×512。若现场仍卡顿，可仅将 <code>MELODY_BUF_COUNT</code> 提到 6（播放时约 6KB），<strong>不要</strong>恢复 16KB 静态 BSS。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>DAC 独占</strong>：蜂鸣与旋律仍共用 <code>\"sound\"</code> 设备，由 <code>audio_th</code> 命令互斥。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>打印线程</strong>：<code>mqtt_prn</code> 栈 6144；创建失败优先查 TCM 剩余空间，而非误认为 MQTT 协议错误。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>重复源文件</strong>：曾存在 <code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c</code> 与 <code>binary_rx/</code> 下重复实现，已删除父目录副本，以 <code>binary_rx/mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c</code> 为准。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"8-验证建议\">8. 验证建议<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#8-验证建议\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>音量</strong>：<code>volumeSet</code> 只改变等待旋律；按键声保持 65。  </li>\n<li><strong>旋律质量</strong>：生图等待全程无规律杂音；停止后无残留 DAC 占用。  </li>\n<li><strong>收图打印</strong>：日志出现 <code>binary result ok</code> 后应能 <code>print thread dispatched</code>，无 <code>create print thread failed</code>。  </li>\n<li><strong>误报</strong>：不应再因 <code>audioChunk</code> 成功而出现 <code>rx dispatch failed</code>（除非真正 dispatch 返回非 0）。  </li>\n<li><strong>内存</strong>：对比烧录前后 <code>list_memheap</code> 或 map 中 <code>_empty_ram</code> 偏移，确认 BSS 减少约 16KB。</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"9-相关源码路径\">9. 相关源码路径<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#9-相关源码路径\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>用途</th><th>路径</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>蜂鸣/旋律实现</td><td><code>applications/button_control/beep.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>头文件</td><td><code>applications/button_control/beep.h</code></td></tr><tr><td>旋律 PCM</td><td><code>applications/button_control/melody_pcm_data.h</code></td></tr><tr><td>生图等待启停旋律</td><td><code>applications/audio/audio_result_wait.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>收图停旋律 + 起打印</td><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/binary_rx/mqtt_backend_binary_audio_chunk.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>打印线程创建</td><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/binary_rx/mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>同步收包 yield</td><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_async_rx.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>下行模式配置</td><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_config.h</code></td></tr><tr><td>TCM 堆定义</td><td><code>drivers/board.h</code>、<code>drivers/board.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>链接布局</td><td><code>link.lds</code>（<code>_empty_ram</code>、<code>.bss</code> > ram）</td></tr><tr><td>内存 map</td><td><code>out/rtthread.map</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"10-变更摘要相对-2026-05-18\">10. 变更摘要（相对 2026-05-18）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#10-变更摘要相对-2026-05-18\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>项目</th><th>2026-05-18</th><th>2026-05-27</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>旋律播放</td><td>定时 sem 补块</td><td>DMA 乒乓 + <code>tx_complete</code> 背压</td></tr><tr><td>音量</td><td>占位 / 统一 70%</td><td>按键固定 65，旋律 Codec 硬件音量</td></tr><tr><td>旋律缓冲</td><td>未涉及大块 BSS</td><td>8×512 静态 → <strong>4×256 动态池</strong></td></tr><tr><td>TCM</td><td>未分析</td><td>释放 <strong>16KB</strong> 常驻，修复打印线程 OOM</td></tr><tr><td>MQTT</td><td>—</td><td>同步 yield、关闭 async RX、修正误报日志</td></tr><tr><td><code>audio_th</code> 优先级</td><td>27</td><td><strong>14</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<p><em>文档整理日期：2026-05-27；对应工程：<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd_bz</code>。</em></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01\">AI 打印机固件 — 项目开发记录总纲</a></li>\n</ul>","n